ctProfile.asp?id=14658 eXenewable Project Profile Page - La Magascona, PV, Spain]</ref>
The Magasquila photovoltaic power station covers {{convert|70|ha}} and it has a peak output of 11.52&nbsp;MW. It was commissioned in June 2008.<ref name=exenewable14658/>
